trans-unit.source: Represents the addition of a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> during dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Representerar för att lägga till en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> vid dynamisk uppdatering.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used by a tracking service to determine which <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s have been added during a dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan användas av en spårningstjänst för för att avgöra vilka <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s har lagts till under en dynamisk uppdatering.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: An instance of this object is generated for every <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet> that is added (that is, that did not exist in the workflow prior to this dynamic update).
trans-unit.target: En instans av det här objektet skapas för varje <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>som har lagts till (det vill säga som fanns inte i arbetsflödet innan den här dynamisk uppdatering).</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"></xref> class by using the new <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av den nya <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> is a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> är en null-referens (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the new <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref>.
